snippet.title: Justice for Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
A recently released audio recording of Actress Amber Heard admitting to her abuse of Actor Johnny Depp during their relationship sheds much-needed light on the plight of male victims of domestic violence. 

National Domestic Violence Hotline
Advocates are available 24/7 at 1-800-799-SAFE (7233) in more than 200 languages. All calls are free and confidential.

https://malesurvivor.org/
Provides resources to male survivors of sexual trauma.

https://www.safeaustin.org/
Provides services and shelter for male victims of sexual assault and domestic violence. They can help you locate shelters in your area, where available.
